  "title": "company driver",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Description</strong></u></p><p>The Company Driver is responsible for ensuring the\nsafe journey of key management staff between the designated locations. </p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Possess safe driving practices</li><li>Planning of routes to ensure management staff arrives at meeting venues on time</li><li>Upkeep cleanliness of vehicle, both internal and external</li><li>Perform checks and conduct daily vehicle services and maintenance</li><li>Collect and ensure timely delivery of internal documents between various offices</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties which may be assigned from time to time</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at Class 3 driving license.</li><li>Able to read, write and communicate with simple English</li><li>Familiar with the traffic rules and regulations</li><li>Positive attitude with good interpersonal skills</li><li>Willing to work long hours when required</li><li>Ability to work in a dynamic and fast paced environment</li></ul>",
